        Constructor Do FFT and necessary process for parameter calculation in class function
        Parameters:
        capWaveI - raw data I captured by AGPIO WSMX HSDGT
        capWaveQ - raw data Q captured by AGPIO WSMX HSDGT
        signalBinCount - odd bin number to calculate spectrum power integration
        noiseStartFrequency - start frequency of noise floor
        noiseStopFrequency - stop frequency of noise floor
